xt":"◎hardworking gardener勤奋的园丁"},{"type":"entry","text":"Libra [ˈliːbrə]","headword":"Libra"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.天秤座（9月23日~10月23日）"},{"type":"entry","text":"Scorpio [ˈskɔːpiəʊ]","headword":"Scorpio"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.天蝎座（10月24日~11月22日）"}]},{"number":669,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"possessive [pəˈzesɪv]","headword":"possessive"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.占有欲强的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be possessive about对…有占有欲"},{"type":"entry","text":"determined [dɪˈtɜːmɪnd]","headword":"determined"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.矢志不渝的"},{"type":"entry","text":"self-centred [ˌself ˈsentəd]","headword":"self-centred"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.以自我为中心的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎self-centred attitude以自我为中心的态度"},{"type":"entry","text":"Sagittarius [ˌsædʒɪˈteəriəs]","headword":"Sagittarius"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.射手座（11月23日~12月21日）"},{"type":"entry","text":"happy-go-lucky [ˌhæpi ɡəʊ ˈlʌki]","headword":"happy-go-lucky"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.逍遥自在的"},{"type":"entry","text":"boastful [ˈbəʊstfl]","headword":"boastful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.自负的"},{"type":"entry","text":"Capricornus [ˌkæprɪˈkɔːnəs]","headword":"Capricornus"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.摩羯座（12月22日~1月19日）"},{"type":"entry","text":"Aquarius [əˈkweəriəs]","headword":"Aquarius"}]},{"number":670,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.水瓶座（1月20日~2月18日）"},{"type":"entry","text":"Pisces [ˈpaɪsiːz]","headword":"Pisces"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.双鱼座（2月19日~3月20日）"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"Horoscope–Aries星座密语–白羊座"},{"type":"text","text":"You Rams are notoriously impatient, especially when it comes to"},{"type":"text","text":"romance. Cut to the chase by venturing out of familiar territory. Concert"},{"type":"text","text":"halls, theaters and museums are all good places for you to find love. Aries"},{"type":"example","text":"could also meet someone special at an art class or dance club. If you’re the"},{"type":"example","text":"athletic type, try jogging on a popular beach or taking a hot-box yoga class."},{"type":"text","text":"白羊座是出了名的没有耐心，尤其是在感情方面。你可以将追求"},{"type":"text","text":"地点选在熟悉的地点。音乐厅、电影院和博物馆都是寻觅爱情的理想"}]},{"number":671,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"地点。你还有可能在艺术班或者舞蹈俱乐部里遇到那个特别的人。如"},{"type":"text","text":"果你是运动型的，不妨尝试去附近有名的海滩慢跑或是去上高温瑜伽"},{"type":"text","text":"课。"}]}]}